<Link id="l00274" /><CodeLine lineNumber="274"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00275" /><CodeLine lineNumber="275"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// This class is intentionally packed into a 32b value as it is used as a</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00276" /><CodeLine lineNumber="276"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// MVT::i32 ConstantSDNode SDValue for SelectionDAG and as immediate operands</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00277" /><CodeLine lineNumber="277"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// on INLINEASM and INLINEASM&#95;BR MachineInstr&#39;s.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00278" /><CodeLine lineNumber="278"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00279" /><CodeLine lineNumber="279"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// The encoding of Flag is currently:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00280" /><CodeLine lineNumber="280"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   Bits 2-0  - A Kind::&#42; value indicating the kind of the operand.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00281" /><CodeLine lineNumber="281"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//               (KindField)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00282" /><CodeLine lineNumber="282"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   Bits 15-3 - The number of SDNode operands associated with this inline</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00283" /><CodeLine lineNumber="283"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//               assembly operand. Once lowered to MIR, this represents the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00284" /><CodeLine lineNumber="284"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//               number of MachineOperands necessary to refer to a</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00285" /><CodeLine lineNumber="285"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//               MachineOperandType::MO&#95;FrameIndex. (NumOperands)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00286" /><CodeLine lineNumber="286"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   Bit 31    - Determines if this is a matched operand. (IsMatched)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00287" /><CodeLine lineNumber="287"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   If bit 31 is set:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00288" /><CodeLine lineNumber="288"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//     Bits 30-16 - The operand number that this operand must match.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00289" /><CodeLine lineNumber="289"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//                  (MatchedOperandNo)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00290" /><CodeLine lineNumber="290"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   Else if bits 2-0 are Kind::Mem:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00291" /><CodeLine lineNumber="291"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//     Bits 30-16 - A ConstraintCode:: value indicating the original</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00292" /><CodeLine lineNumber="292"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//                  constraint code. (MemConstraintCode)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00293" /><CodeLine lineNumber="293"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   Else:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00294" /><CodeLine lineNumber="294"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//     Bits 29-16 - The register class ID to use for the operand. (RegClass)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00295" /><CodeLine lineNumber="295"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//     Bit  30    - If the register is permitted to be spilled.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00296" /><CodeLine lineNumber="296"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//                  (RegMayBeFolded)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00297" /><CodeLine lineNumber="297"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//                  Defaults to false &quot;r&quot;, may be set for constraints like</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00298" /><CodeLine lineNumber="298"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//                  &quot;rm&quot; (or &quot;g&quot;).</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00299" /><CodeLine lineNumber="299"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00300" /><CodeLine lineNumber="300"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   As such, MatchedOperandNo, MemConstraintCode, and</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00301" /><CodeLine lineNumber="301"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   (RegClass+RegMayBeFolded) are views of the same slice of bits, but are</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00302" /><CodeLine lineNumber="302"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   mutually exclusive depending on the fields IsMatched then KindField.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00303" /><CodeLine lineNumber="303" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/inlineasm/flag"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">class </span><span class="doxyHighlight"><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/inlineasm/flag/#a9e9d8e949b5dae1762f3a70898246ccd">Flag</a> &#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00304" /><CodeLine lineNumber="304"><span class="doxyHighlight">    uint32&#95;t Storage;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00305" /><CodeLine lineNumber="305"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">using </span><span class="doxyHighlight">KindField = <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/bitfield/element">Bitfield::Element&lt;Kind, 0, 3, Kind::Func&gt;</a>;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00306" /><CodeLine lineNumber="306"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">using </span><span class="doxyHighlight">NumOperands = <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/bitfield/element">Bitfield::Element&lt;unsigned, 3, 13&gt;</a>;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00307" /><CodeLine lineNumber="307"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">using </span><span class="doxyHighlight">MatchedOperandNo = <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/bitfield/element">Bitfield::Element&lt;unsigned, 16, 15&gt;</a>;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00308" /><CodeLine lineNumber="308"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">using </span><span class="doxyHighlight">MemConstraintCode = <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/bitfield/element">Bitfield::Element&lt;ConstraintCode, 16, 15, ConstraintCode::Max&gt;</a>;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00309" /><CodeLine lineNumber="309"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">using </span><span class="doxyHighlight">RegClass = <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/bitfield/element">Bitfield::Element&lt;unsigned, 16, 14&gt;</a>;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00310" /><CodeLine lineNumber="310"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">using </span><span class="doxyHighlight">RegMayBeFolded = <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/bitfield/element">Bitfield::Element&lt;bool, 30, 1&gt;</a>;</span></CodeLine>
